                p.text(class="w-75") Bring everyone together to build better products. Manage makes it simple for software teams to plan day-to-day tasks while keeping the larger team goals in view.
                .demo
                  a.btn(class="px-3 d-flex align-items-center rounded-pill", href="https://yousefel-black.github.io/Manage/")
                    | Demo
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-long ps-2")
          div(class="carousel-item")
            .item-content(class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row gap-4 align-items-center")
              .image(class="col-md-6")
                img(class="img-fluid", src="imgs/bookmark.jpg")
              .content(class="d-flex d-md-block flex-column align-items-center")
                h4.title(class="py-3") Bookmark
                p.text(class="w-75") A Simple Bookmark Manager. A clean and simple interface to organize your favourite websites. Open a new browser tab and see your sites load instantly. Try it for free.
                .demo
                  a.btn(class="px-3 d-flex align-items-center rounded-pill", href="https://yousefel-black.github.io/Bookmark/")
                    | Demo
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-long ps-2")
          div(class="carousel-item")
            .item-content(class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row gap-4 align-items-center")
              .image(class="col-md-6")
                img(class="img-fluid", src="imgs/blogr.jpg")
              .content(class="d-flex d-md-block flex-column align-items-center")
                h4.title(class="py-3") Blogr
                p.text(class="w-75") A modern publishing platform. Grow your audience and build your online brand
                .demo
                  a.btn(class="px-3 d-flex align-items-center rounded-pill", href="https://yousefel-black.github.io/Blogr/")
                    | Demo
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-long ps-2")
          div(class="carousel-item")
            .item-content(class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row gap-4 align-items-center")
              .image(class="col-md-6")
                img(class="img-fluid", src="imgs/easybank.jpg")
              .content(class="d-flex d-md-block flex-column align-items-center")
                h4.title(class="py-3") Easybank
                p.text(class="w-75") Next generation digital banking. Take your financial life online. Your Easybank account will be a one-stop-shop for spending, saving, budgeting, investing, and much more.
                .demo
                  a.btn(class="px-3 d-flex align-items-center rounded-pill", href="https://yousefel-black.github.io/Easybank/")
                    | Demo
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-long ps-2")
        button(class="carousel-control-prev", type="button", data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators", data-bs-slide="prev")
          span(class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true")
          span(class="visually-hidden") Previous
        button(class="carousel-control-next", type="button", data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators", data-bs-slide="next")
          span(class="carousel-control-next-icon", aria-hidden="true")
          span(class="visually-hidden") Next

